===Noun===
{{en-noun|gasmen}}

# {{lb|en|colloquial}} A worker for a company that supplies [[gas]] (in the sense of the gaseous fuel), especially one who visits premises to read the meter, test appliances etc.
#: {{ux|en|I spent all morning waiting for the '''gasman''' to call.}}
# A man employed in the [[manufacture]] of [[gas]].
# The man who controls the [[light]]s of the [[stage]]. <!--now obsolete?-->
# {{lb|en|slang}} A [[worthless]] person (male)

